\f0\fs29\fsmilli14667 To be honest, I don\'92t know if I want to keep this moment in. This moment meant so much to me that I don\'92t want to use it to make a point. I didn\'92t find it strange that my mother FaceTimed me. It was really nice, and I\'92m glad that I was able to witness both my grandmother and my mother in that moment. I think about it a lot, though, and feel grateful for mostly my mom, but also for Facetime.\'a0
