\f0\fs29\fsmilli14667 Even if they happen in deeply familiar locations, it feels like these moments of great import are always taking place in random locations with random objects and random people around you. Banal logistics, systems, and (now) platforms that shape both our socio-economic order and our minute-to-minute, gesture-to-gesture living.
\f1\fs24 \
